description:
In the words of Chris Pratt, Guardians of Galaxy director James Gunn "runs deep." How did he get the GOTG gig? What inspired his vision for the franchise? And what in the world is a "bukake"? James answers all these questions and more in Part 1 of this week's episode. Anna and James also bond over their competitive spirits, love of cream of wheat, and of course, their shared affection for Chris Pratt. And stay tuned 'til the end when Anna and James exchange outrageous Chat Roulette prank stories. Trust us, you'll be shocked!  Come back tomorrow for Part 2, when Anna, Sim, and James help a caller work through a tricky family situation.

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
